title: FC/Kahuna - Machine Says Yes (UK Release / LOSSLESS / WAV)
description:
This is an extremely rare CD including "Hayling," featuring the vocals of Hafdis Huld of "Gus Gus."  I have not found it available in the U.S., so I went outside the confines of the US to get it.  Good stuff.  Certified clean of any "nasties," at least by me (having originated the torrent).

All files are in .wav format.  I simply ripped the CD using Exact Audio Copy and simply put it into a ZIP file with no compression at all (used "Store" setting on WinRAR).  Better than FLAC!

Enjoy.
